"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7a033b0d80945ae030a5b0a13fa5769c53a3c6","tid":562363,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食反平時街邊食的野。<br />\n價錢貴4-5倍。<br />\n仲要排長龍。等的時間起碼10倍。<br />\n<br />\n我寧願日日食杯面。<br />\n等初7/8出街慢慢食。</blockquote>係咪4,5倍咁誇張呀<br />\n一個砵仔糕4,50蚊，一串魚蛋又4,50蚊咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平時元朗買⋯ <br />\n砵仔糕，$12/5個⋯<br />\n深水埗龍_小食，魚蛋$9 買一送一⋯<br />\n<br />\n等的時間無得辯論掛？"},{"pid":"e46129388ec192ebd3370be267c1e7e66c6cabd1","tid":562363,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食反平時街邊食的野。<br />\n價錢貴4-5倍。<br />\n仲要排長龍。等的時間起碼10倍。<br />\n<br />\n我寧願日日食杯面。<br />\n等初7/8出街慢慢食。</blockquote>年廿九三十 我行勻屯天元就係為左搞掂初一至初八的食糧</blockquote><br />\n我e幾日出街，只夠膽食麥記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我認我窮⋯<br />\n<br />\n屋企附近2間茶記，<br />\n一間每個餐加$10。<br />\n一間唔計餐再加一。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b910083639211a022f257561018ccdd82ca4203","tid":562363,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T00:00:04.000Z","msg":"忍幾日姐"},{"pid":"09bec22e30f2057be2ec964c8d79453e94cf110e","tid":562363,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}